quran[399]{c,v,t}:
  51,31,"Ibrahim ne kaha “aey farstaadgaan-e-ilaahi (envoys), kya mohim aapko dar-pesh hai"
  51,32,Unhon ne kaha “hum ek mujrim qaum ki taraf bheje gaye hain
  51,33,Taa-ke uspar paki hui mitti ke patthar (clay-stones) barsa de
  51,34,Jo aapke Rubb ke haan hadd se guzar jane walon ke liye nishan zada hain”
  51,35,Phir humne un sab logon ko nikal liya jo us basti mein momin thay
  51,36,Aur wahan humne ek ghar ke siwa musalmano ka koi ghar na paya
  51,37,Uske baad humne wahan bas ek nishani un logon ke liye chodh di jo dardnaak azaab se darte hon
  51,38,Aur (tumhare liye nishani hai) Moosa ke qissey mein jab humne usey sareeh sanad (clear authority) ke saath Firoun ke paas bheja
  51,39,To woh apne bal-bootay par akad gaya aur bola yeh jaadugar hai ya majnoon(deewana) hai
  51,40,Aakhir-e-kaar humne usey aur uske lashkaron ko pakda aur sabko samandar mein phenk diya aur woh malamat zadah hokar reh gaya
  51,41,"Aur (tumhare liye nishani hai) Aad (people of Aad) mein, jabke humne unpar ek aisi hi bay-khair(devastating) hawa bhej di"
  51,42,Ke jis cheez par bhi woh guzar gayi usey boseeda (rotten) karke rakh diya
  51,43,"Aur (tumhare liye nishani hai) Samood mein, jab unse kaha gaya tha ke ek khaas waqt tak mazey karlo"
  51,44,Magar is tambeeh(warning) par bhi unhon ne apne Rubb ke hukum se sartabi (brazenly disobey) ki. Aakhir-e-kar unke dekhte dekhte ek achanak toot padne waley azaab ne unko aa liya
  51,45,Phir na unmein uthne ki sakat thi aur na woh apna bachao kar sakte thay
  51,46,Aur in sabse pehle humne Nooh ki qaum ko halaak kiya kyunke woh fasiq (wicked) log thay
  51,47,Aasman ko humne apne zoar se banaya hai aur hum iski qudrat rakhte hain
  51,48,Zameen ko humne bichaya hai aur hum badey acchey hamwar(Smoothers/ spread) karne waley hain
  51,49,"Aur har cheez ke humne jodey banaye hain, shayad ke tum ussey sabaq lo"
  51,50,"To daudo Allah ki taraf , main tumahre liye us ki taraf se saaf saaf khabardar karne wala hoon"
  51,51,Aur na banao Allah ke saath koi dusra mabood. Main tumahre liye uski taraf se saaf saaf khabardar karne wala hoon
  51,52,"Yunhi hota raha hai, inse pehle ki qaumon ke paas bhi koi Rasool aisa nahin aaya jisey unhon ne yeh na kaha ho ke yeh saahir (sorcerer) hai ya majnoon(deewana)"
  51,53,"Kya in sab ne apas mein ispar koi samjhauta karliya hai? Nahin, balke yeh sab sarkash log hain"
  51,54,"Pas aey Nabi, inse rukh pher lo, tumpar kuch malamat nahin"
  51,55,"Albatta nasihat karte raho, kyunke nasihat imaan laney walon ke liye nafeh(faiyda-mand) hai"
  51,56,Maine Jinn aur Insano ko iske siwa kisi kaam ke liye paida nahin kiya hai ke woh meri bandagi karein
  51,57,Main unsey koi rizq nahin chahta aur na yeh chahta hoon ke woh mujhey khilayein
  51,58,"Allah to khud hi Razzak hai, badi quwwat wala aur zabardast"
  51,59,"Pas jin logon ne zulm kiya hai unke hissey ka bhi waisa hi azaab tayyar hai jaisa inhi jaise logon ko unke hissey ka mil chuka hai, iske liye yeh log jaldi na machayein"
  51,60,Aakhir ko tabahi hai kufr karne walon ke liye us roz jiska inhein khauff dilaya jaa raha hai
  52,1,Kasam hai Tur (Mount) ki
  52,2,Aur ek aisi khuli kitaab ki
  52,3,Jo raqeeq jild(fine parchment) mein likkhi hui hai
  52,4,Aur aabaad (much-frequented) ghar ki
  52,5,Aur unchi chatt (canopy) ki
  52,6,Aur maujzan samandar (swelling sea) ki
  52,7,Ke tere Rubb ka azaab zaroor waqeh honay wala hai
  52,8,Jisey koi dafa karne wala nahin
  52,9,Woh us roz waqeh hoga jab aasmaan buri tarah dagmagayega
  52,10,Aur pahad udey udey phirenge
  52,11,Tabahi hai us roz un jhutlane walon ke liye
  52,12,Jo aaj khel ke taur par apni hujjat baaziyon mein lagey huey hain
  52,13,Jis din unhein dhakke maar maar kar naar-e-jahannum (fire of hell) ki taraf le chala jayega
  52,14,Us waqt unse kaha jayega ke “ yeh wahi aag hai jisey tum jhutlaya karte thay
  52,15,Ab batao yeh jaadu hai ya tumhein soojh nahin raha hai
  52,16,"Jao ab jhulso iske andar, tum khwa sabr karo ya na karo, tumhare liye yaksan hai, tumhein waisa hi badla diya ja raha hai jaise tum amal kar rahey thay"
  52,17,Muttaqi log wahan baagon (gardens) aur niyamaton mein hongey
  52,18,"Lutf le rahe hongey un cheezon se jo unka Rubb unhein dega, aur unka Rubb unhein dozakh ke azaab se bacha lega"
  52,19,(Unse kaha jayega) khao aur peo mazey se apne un aamaal ke siley mein jo tum karte rahey ho
  52,20,Woh aamne saamne bichey huey takhaton(thrones) par takiye(couches) lagaye baithey hongey aur hum khoobsurat aankhon waali hoorein unse biyah (marry) denge
  52,21,Jo log imaan laaye hain aur unki aulad bhi kisi darja-e-imaan mein unke naksh-e-qadam par chali hai unki us aulad ko bhi hun (jannat mein) unke saath mila denge aur unke amaal mein koi ghaata(loss) unko na denge. Har shaks apne kasb ke aevaz rehan hai.( Every person is pledged to what he did)
  52,22,"Hum unko har tarah ke phal (fruits) aur gosht , jis cheez ko bhi unka ji chahega khoob diye chale jayenge"
  52,23,Wahan woh ek dusre se jaam-e-sharaab lapak lapak kar le rahey hongey jis mein na yawa-goyi (ill speech) hogi na bad-kirdari
  52,24,"Aur unki khidmat mein woh ladke daudte (running) phir rahey hongey jo unhi ke liye makhsoos hongey, aisey khoobsurat jaise chupa kar rakkhe huey moti(pearls)"
  52,25,Yeh log apas mein ek dusre se (duniya mein guzre huey) halaat puchenge
  52,26,Yeh kahenge ke hum pehle apne ghar waalon mein darte huey zindagi basar karte thay
  52,27,Aakhir e kaar Allah ne hum par fazl farmaya aur humein jhulsa dene wali hawa ke azaab se bacha liya
  52,28,"Hum pichli zindagi mein usi se duaein maangte thay, woh waqai bada hi Mohsin (beneficent) aur Raheem hai"
  52,29,"Pas aey nabi, tum nasihat kiye jao, apne Rubb ke fazal se na tum kaahin (soothsayer) ho aur na majnoon (madman)"
  52,30,Kya yeh log kehte hain ke yeh shaks shayar hai jiske haqq mein hum gardish-e-ayyam (misfortune) ke intizaar kar rahe hain
  52,31,"Inse kaho, accha intizaar karo, main bhi tumhare saath intizaar karta hoon"
  52,32,Kya inki aqalein(minds) inhein aisi hi baatein karne ke liye kehti hain? Ya dar-haqeeqat yeh inaad (transgression)mein hadd se guzare huey log hain
  52,33,Kya ye kehte hain ke is shaks ne yeh quraan khud ghad (invented/fabricated) liya hai? Asal baat yeh hai ke yeh imaan nahin lana chahte
  52,34,Agar yeh apne is qaul (saying) mein sacche hain to isi shaan ka ek kalaam bana layein
  52,35,Kya yeh kisi khaliq ke bagair khud paida ho gaye hain? Ya yeh khud apne khaliq hain
  52,36,Ya zameen aur aasmaano ko inhon ne paida kiya hai? Asal baat yeh hai ke yeh yaqeen nahin rakhte
  52,37,Kya tere Rubb ke khazane in ke kabze mein hain? Ya un par inhi ka hukum chalta hai
  52,38,Kya inke paas koi seedi(ladder) hai jispar chadh kar yeh ilm-e-baala ki sun-gun letey hain? In mein se jisne sun-gun li ho woh laaye ko khuli daleel
  52,39,Kya Allah ke liye to hain betiyan aur tum logon ke liye hain betay (sons)
  52,40,Kya tum insey koi ajar maangte ho key eh zabardasti padi hui chatti ke bojh taley dabey jatey hain (burdened with a load of debt)
  52,41,Kya inke paas gaib ke haqaiq ka ilm hai ke uski bina par yeh likh rahe hoon
  52,42,Kya yeh koi chaal chalna chahte hain? (agar yeh baat hai) to kufr karne walon par in ki chaal ulti hi padegi
  52,43,Kya Allah ke siwa yeh koi aur maabood rakhte hain? Allah paak hai us shirk se jo yeh log kar rahey hain
  52,44,Yeh log aasmaan ke tukde bhi girte huye dekh lein to kahenge yeh baadal hain jo umdey chale aa rahe hain
  52,45,"Pas aey nabi, inhein inke haal par chodh do yahan tak ke yeh apne us din ko pahunch jayein jismein yeh maar giraye jayenge"
  52,46,Jis din na inki apni koi chaal inke kisi kaam aayegi na koi inki madad ko aayega
  52,47,"Aur us waqt ke aane se pehle bhi zalimon ke liye ek azaab hai, magar in mein se aksar jaante nahin hain"
  52,48,"Aey Nabi , apne Rubb ka faisla aane tak sabr karo. Tum hamari nigaah mein ho. Tum jab utho to apne Rubb ki hamd ke saath uski tasbeeh karo"
  52,49,Raat ko bhi uski tasbeeh kiya karo aur sitare jab palat-te hain us waqt bhi
  53,1,Kasam hai taare ki jabke woh guroob hua
  53,2,Tumhara rafeeq(companion) na bhatka hai na behka(deluded) hai
  53,3,Woh apni khwaish-e-nafs se nahin bolta
  53,4,Yeh to ek wahee (Inspiration /revelation) hai jo uspar nazil ki jati hai
  53,5,Usey zabardast quwwat waley ne taleem di hai
  53,6,Jo bada sahib-e-hikmat hai
  53,7,Woh saamne aa khada hua jabke woh balaii ufuq par tha(highest part of the horizon)
  53,8,Phir kareeb aaya aur upar muallak ho gaya.(approached and descended)
  53,9,Yahan tak ke do kamano (bow lengths) ke barabar ya issey kuch kam faasla reh gaya
  53,10,Tab usne Allah ke banday ko wahee (revelation) pahunchayi jo wahee (revelation) bhi usey pahunchani thi
  53,11,"Nazar ne jo kuch dekha, dil ne usmein jhoot na milaya"
  53,12,Ab kya tum us cheez par ussey jhagadte ho jisey woh aankhon se dekhta hai
  53,13,Aur ek martaba phir usney
  53,14,Sidratul muntaha ke paas usko (Angel Gibriel) dekha
  53,15,Jahan paas hi jannat-ul-maawa hai
  53,16,Us waqt sidrah par chaa raha tha jo kuch ke chaa raha tha
  53,17,Nigaah na chundhyayi (waver / swerve) na hadd se mutajawiz (transgress) hui
  53,18,Aur usney apne Rubb ki badi badi nishaniyan dekhi
  53,19,"Ab zara batao , tumne kabhi is Laat aur is Uzza (names of pagan idols)"
  53,20,Aur tisri (third) ek aur devi Manaat ki haqeeqat par kuch gaur bhi kiya
  53,21,Kya betay (sons) tumhare liye hain aur betiyan (daughters) khuda ke liye
  53,22,Yeh to badi dhandhli (unjust/unfair) ki taqseem hui
  53,23,"Darasal yeh kuch nahin hain magar bas chandh naam jo tumne aur tumhare baap dada ne rakh liye hain. Allah ne inke liye koi sanad nazil nahin ki. Haqeeat yeh hai ke log mehez weham-o-gumaan ki pairvi kar rahey hain aur khwahishaat-e-nafs ke mureed bane huey hain, halanke unke Rubb ki taraf se unke paas hidayat aa chuki hai"
  53,24,Kya insaan jo kuch chaahe uske liye wahi haqq hai
  53,25,Duniya aur aakhirat ka maalik to Allah hi hai
  53,26,"Aasmano mein kitne hi farishte maujood hain, un ki shafaat (intercession) kuch bhi kaam nahin aa sakti jab tak ke Allah kisi aisey shaks ke haqq mein uski ijazat na dey jiske liye woh koi arzdaasht (plea) sunna chahe aur usko pasand karey"
  53,27,Magar jo log aakhirat ko nahin maante woh farishton ko deviyon (godess) ke naamo se mausoom karte hain
  53,28,"Halaanke is maamle ka koi ilm (knowledge) unhein haasil nahin hai. Woh mehez gumaan ki pairvi kar rahey hain, aur gumaan haqq ki jagah kuch bhi kaam nahin de sakta"
  53,29,"Pas aey Nabi, jo shaks hamarey zikr se mooh pherta hai, aur duniya ki zindagi ke siwa jise kuch matloob nahin hai, usey uske haal par chodh do"
  53,30,"In logon ka mablag-e-ilm (utmost of their knowledge) bas yahi kuch hai, yeh baat tera Rubb hi zyada jaanta hai ke uske raaste se kaun bhatak gaya hai aur kaun seedhe raaste par hai"
  53,31,Aur zameen aur aasmaano ki har cheez ka maalik Allah hi hai. Taa-ke Allah burayi karne waalon ko unke amal ka badla de aur un logon ko acchi jaza se nawaze jinhon ne neik rawayya ikhtiyar kiya hai
  53,32,"Jo badey badey gunahon aur khule khule qabeeh afaal (shameful deeds) se parheiz karte hain, illa yeh ke kuch kasoor unse sarzad ho jaye. Bila shubhah tere Rubb ka daaman-e-magfirat bahut waseeh hai. Woh tumhein us waqt se khoob jaanta hai jab usne zameen se tumhein paida kiya, aur jab tum apni maaon (mothers) ke paiton (wombs) mein abhi janin (fetuses) hi thay. Pas apne nafs ki paaki ke daawe na karo. Wahi behtar jaanta hai ke waqai muttaqi kaun hai"
  53,33,"Phir aey Nabi, tumne us shaks ko bhi dekha jo raah-e-khuda se phir gaya"
  53,34,Aur thoda sa de kar ruk gaya
  53,35,Kya uske paas gaib ka ilm hai ke woh haqeeqat ko dekh raha hai
  53,36,Kya usey un baaton ki koi khabar nahin pahunchi jo moosa ke sahifon
  53,37,Aur us Ibrahim ke sahifon mein bayan hui hai jisne wafa ka haqq ada kar diya
  53,38,Yeh ke koi bojh uthane wala dusre ka bojh nahin uthayega
  53,39,Aur yeh ke Insaan ke liye kuch nahin hai magar woh jiski usne saii(koshish /Strive) ki hai
  53,40,Aur yeh ke uski saii (koshih/strive/effort) anqareeb dekhi jayegi
  53,41,Aur uski puri jaza use di jayegi
  53,42,Aur yeh ke aakhir-e-kaar pahunchna tere Rubb hi ke paas hai
  53,43,Aur yeh ke usi ne hasaya aur usi ne rulaya
  53,44,Aur yeh ke usi ne maut di aur usi ne zindagi bakshi
  53,45,Aur yeh ke usi ne narr (male) aur maada (female) ka joda paida kiya
  53,46,Ek boond (sperm-drop) se jab woh tapkayi jati hai
  53,47,Aur yeh ke dusri zindagi bakshna bhi usi ke zimme hai
  53,48,Aur yeh ke usi ne gani (enriches) kiya aur jaidad bakshi
  53,49,Aur yeh ke wahi sheraa (Sirius / mighty star) ka Rubb hai
  53,50,Aur yeh ke usi ne Aad-e-oola (people of Aad) ko halaak kiya
  53,51,Aur samood ko aisa mitaya ke unmein se kisi ko baaki na choda
  53,52,Aur unse pehle qaum-e-Nooh ko tabaah kiya kyunke woh thay hi sakht zaalim-o-sarkash log
  53,53,Aur aundhi girne wali bastiyon ko utha phenka. (Qaum-e-Lut)
  53,54,Phir chaa diya unpar woh kuch jo (tum jaante hi ho ke) kya chaa diya
  53,55,"Pas aey mukhatib, apne Rubb ki kin kin niyamaton mein tu shakk karega"
  53,56,Yeh ek tambeeh (warning) hai pehle aaye huye tambihaat(warnings) mein se
  53,57,Aane wali ghadi qareeb aa lagi hai
  53,58,Allah ke siwa koi usko hatane wala nahin
  53,59,Ab kya yahi woh baatein hain jinpar tum izhaar- e-taajub karte ho
  53,60,Hanste(laugh) ho aur rotey (weep) nahin ho
  53,61,Aur gaa (singing) bajaa kar inhein taalte ho
  53,62,Jhuk jao Allah ke aagey aur bandagi baja laaoo (ayat-e-sajda)
  54,1,Qayamat ki ghadi kareeb aa gayi aur chaand phatt (split) gaya
  54,2,Magar in logon ka haal yeh hai ke khwa koi nishani dekh lein mooh moadh jaatey hain aur kehte hain yeh to chalta hua jaadu hai
  54,3,Inhon ne (isko bhi) jhutla diya aur apni khwahishat-e-nafs hi ki pairwi ki.Har maamlay ko Aakhir-e-kaar ek anjaam par pahunch kar rehna hai
  54,4,In logon ke saamne (pichle qaumon ke) woh halaat aa chuke hain jinmein sarkashi se baaz rakhne ke liye kafi samaan-e-ibrat hai
  54,5,Aur aisi hikmat jo nasihat ke maqsad ko ba-darja-e-atam (consummate wisdom) pura karti hain magar tambihat(warnings) in par kaargar nahin hoti
  54,6,"Pas aey Nabi, insey rukh pher lo. Jis roz pukarne wala ek sakht nagawaar cheez ki taraf pukarega"
  54,7,Log sehmi hui (down-cast) nigaahon ke saath apni qabraon se is tarah niklenge goya woh bikhri huyi tiddiyan (locusts) hain
  54,8,Pukarne wale ki taraf daudey jaa rahey hongey Aur wahi munkireen (jo duniya mein iska inkar karte thay)us waqt kahenge ke yeh din to bada kathin hai
  54,9,"Insey pehle Nooh ki qaum jhutla chuki hai. Unhon ne hamare bandey ko jhoota karar diya aur kaha ke yeh deewana hai, aur woh buri tarah jhidka (rebuffed) gaya"
  54,10,"Aakhir-e-kaar usne apne Rubb ko pukara ke “main magloob ho chuka , ab tu inse inteqam le”"
  54,11,Tab humne mausla-dhaar baarish se aasmaan ke darwaze khol diye aur zameen ko phaad kar chasmon mein tabdeel kar diya
  54,12,Aur yeh saara paani us kaam ko pura karne ke liye mil gaya jo mukaddar ho chuka tha
  54,13,Aur Nooh ko humne ek takhaton(planks) aur keelon (nails) wali par sawar kar diya
  54,14,Jo hamari nigrani mein chal rahi thi .yeh tha badla us shaks ki khatir jiski na-qadri ki gayi thi
  54,15,"Us kashti ko humne ek nishani bana kar chodh diya, phir koi hai nasihat qabool karne wala"
  54,16,"Dekhlo, kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi thi meri tambihaat (warnings)"
  54,17,"Humne is Quran ko nasihat ke liye aasaan zariya bana diya hai, phir kya hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala"
  54,18,"Aad ne jhutlaya, to dekhlo ke kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi thi meri tambihaat (warnings)"
  54,19,Humne ek paiham nahusat (unremitting misfortune) ke din sakht toofani hawa unpar bhej di jo logon ko utha utha kar is tarah phenk rahi thi
  54,20,Jaise woh jadd (roots) se ukhade huey khajoor ke taney (trunks) hon
  54,21,Pas dekhlo ke kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi thi meri tambihaat (warnings)
  54,22,"Humne is Quran ko nasihat ke liye aasaan zariya bana diya hai, phir kya hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala"
  54,23,Samood ne tambihaat ko jhutlaya
  54,24,Aur kehne lagey “Ek akela aadmi jo hum hi mein se hai kya ab hum uske peechey chalein? Iska ittibaah hum qabool karlein to iske maani yeh hongey ke hum behak gaye hain aur hamari aqal maari gayi hai
  54,25,"Kya hamare darmiyan bas yahi ek shaks tha jispar khuda ka zikr nazil kiya gaya? nahin, balke yeh parle darje ka jhoota aur bar-khud galat (insolent liar)hai”"
  54,26,(Humne apne paigambar se kaha) “ Kal hi inhein maaloom hua jata hai ke kaun parle darje ka jhoota aur bar khud galat hai
  54,27,"Hum ountni (she-camel) ko inke liye fitna bana kar bhej rahe hain, ab zara sabr ke saath dekh ke inka kya anjaam hota hai"
  54,28,Inko jata de ke paani inke aur ountni(she-camel) ke darmiyaan takseem hoga aur har ek apni baari ke din paani par aayega”
  54,29,Aakhir-e-kaar un logon ne apne aadmi ko pukara aur usne is kaam ka beda uthaya aur ountni (she-camel) ko maar dala
  54,30,Phir dekh lo ke kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi thi meri tambeehat (warnings)
  54,31,"Humne unpar bas ek hi dhamaka chodha aur woh baade wale ki rondhi hui baad ke taraah bhus ho kar reh gaya. (Lo! We sent upon them one Shout, and they became as the dry twigs (rejected by) the builder of a cattle-fold"
  54,32,"Humne is Quran ko nasihat ke liye aasaan zariya bana diya hai, ab hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala"
  54,33,Lut ki qaum ne tambihat ko jhutlaya
  54,34,Aur humne pattharao karne wali hawa is par bhej di. Sirf Lut ke ghar wale ussey mehfooz rahe
  54,35,Unko humne apne fazl se raat ke pichle pehar bacha kar nikal diya. Yeh jaza dete hai hum har us shaks ko jo shukar guzar hota hai
  54,36,Lut ne apni qaum ke logon ko hamari pakad se khabardaar kiya magar woh saari tambihat ko mashkuk (doubtful) samajh kar baaton mein udate rahey
  54,37,"Phir unhon ne usey apne mehmano ki hifazat se baaz rakhne ki koshish ki. Aakhir-e-kaar humne unki aankhein moond-di (blinded), ke chakkho ab mera azaab aur meri tambihaat ka maza"
  54,38,Subah sawerey hi ek atal azaab ne unko aa liya
  54,39,Chakkho mazaa ab mere azaab ka aur meri tambihaat ka
  54,40,"Humne is Quran ko nasihat ke liye aasaan zariya bana diya hai, pas hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala"
  54,41,Aur aal-e-Firoun ke paas bhi tambihaat aayi thi
  54,42,Magar unhon ne hamari saari nishaniyon ko jhutla diya. Aakhir ko humne unhein pakda jis taraah koi zabardast qudrat wala pakadta hai
  54,43,Kya tumhare kuffar kuch un logon se behtar hain? Ya aasmani kitaabon mein tumhare liye koi maafi likhi hui hai
  54,44,"Ya in logon ka kehna yeh hai ke hum ek mazboot jattha (jamaat) hain, apna bachao kar lengey"
  54,45,Ankareeb yeh jattha(jamaat) shikhast kha jayega aur yeh sab peeth pheir kar bhaagte nazar aayenge
  54,46,Balke insey nimatne ke liye asal waade ka waqt to qayamat hai aur woh badi aafat aur zyaada talkh-saa-at (badi sakht aur kadwi cheez) hai
  54,47,Yeh mujrim log dar haqeeqat galat fehmi mein mubtala hain aur inki aqal maari gayi hai
  54,48,Jis roz yeh mooh ke bal aag mein ghaseetey jayenge us roz insey kaha jayega ke ab chakkho jahannum ki lapat ka maza
  54,49,Humne har cheez ek taqdeer ke saath paida ki hai
  54,50,Aur hamara hukum bas ek hi hukum hota hai aur palak jhapakate (twinkling of an eye) woh amal mein aa jata hai
  54,51,Tum jaisey bahut-soon ko hum halak kar chuke hain. Phir hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala
  54,52,Jo kuch inhon ne kiya hai woh sab daftaron (office) mein darj hai
  54,53,Aur har choti badi baat likhi hui maujood hai
  54,54,Nafarmani se parhez karne waley yaqeenan baaghon aur neharon mein hongey
  54,55,"Sacchi izzat ki jagah, badey zeeh-iqtedar baadshah ke kareeb"
  55,1,Rahman ne
  55,2,Is Quran ki taleem di hai
  55,3,Usi ne Insan ko paida kiya
  55,4,Aur usey bolna sikhaya
  55,5,Suraj aur chand ek hisaab ke paband hain
  55,6,Aur taarey aur darakht sab sajda-reiz hain
  55,7,Aasman ko usne buland kiya aur mizan qayam kardi
  55,8,Iska taqaza yeh hai ke tum mizaan mein khalal na daalo
  55,9,Insaaf ke saath theek theek tolo (weigh) aur tarazu mein dandi (skimp ) na maaro
  55,10,Zameen ko usne sab makhlooqat (creatures) ke liye banaya
  55,11,"Usmein har tarah ke ba-kasrat laziz phal hain,khajoor ke darakht hain jinke phal ghilafon (sheaths) mein liptey huey hain"
  55,12,Tarah tarah ke galley(corn) hain jinmein bhusa bhi hota hai aur dana (grain) bhi
  55,13,"Pas aey jinn-o-Ins (insan), tum apne Rubb ki kin kin niyamaton ko jhutlaogey"
  55,14,"Insan ko usne thikri (potter) jaise sukhey sadey (rotten) huey gaarey se banaya (clay like [that of] pottery"
  55,15,Aur Jinn ko aag ki lapat se paida kiya
  55,16,"Pas aey Jinn-o-Ins (insan), tum apne Rubb ke kin kin ajaib-e-qudrat ko jhutlaogey"
  55,17,"Dono mashriq aur dono magrib, Sab ka maalik-o-parwardigar wahi hai"
  55,18,"Pas aey jinn-o-Ins, tum apne Rubb ke kin kin qudraton ko jhutlaogey"
  55,19,Do samandaron (seas) ko usne chodh diya ke baham mil jayein
  55,20,Phir bhi unke darmiyan ek purdah hayal(barrier) hai jissey woh tajawuz (transgress) nahin karte
  55,21,"Pas aey jinn-o-Ins (insan), Tum apne Rubb ki qudrat ke kin kin karishmo ko jhutlaogey"
  55,22,In samandaron se Moti aur mongay (coral) nikalte hain
  55,23,"Pas aey jinn-o-Ins (insan), tum apne Rubb ki qudrat ke kin kin kamalaat ko jhutlaogey"
  55,24,Aur yeh jahaaz (ships) usi ke hain jo samandar mein pahadon (mountains) ki tarah unchey uthey huey hain
  55,25,"Pas aye jinn-o-Ins (insan), tum apne Rub ke kin kin ehsanaat ko jhutlaogey"
  55,26,Har cheez jo is zameen par hai fanaa (perish) ho janey wali hai
  55,27,Aur sirf tere Rubb ki jalil-o-kareem zaat hi baaki rehne wali hai
  55,28,"Pas aey jinn-o-Ins (insan), tum apne Rubb ke qudraton ke kin kin kamalaat ko jhutlaogey"
  55,29,"Zameen aur Aasmano mein jo bhi hai sab apni haajatein (needs) usi se maang rahey hain, har aan woh nayi shaan mein hai"
  55,30,"Pas aey jinn-o-Ins (insan), tum apne Rubb ki kin kin siffat-e-hameeda ko jhutlaogey"
  55,31,"Aey zameen ke bojho(loads), ankareeb hum tumse baaz purs (questioning) karne ke liye faarig huey jatey hain"
  55,32,(phir dekh lenge ke) tum apne Rubb ke kin kin ehsanaat ko jhutlate ho
  55,33,"Aey giroh-e-jinn-o-Ins(insan) , gar tum zameen aur aasmano ki sarhadon se nikal kar bhaag sakte ho to bhaag dekho , nahin bhaag sakte iske liye bada zoar chahiye"
  55,34,Apne Rubb ki kin kin qudraton ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,35,(Bhaagne ki koshish karogey to ) Tumpar aag ka shola aur dhoowan (smoke) chodh diya jayega jiska tum muqabla na kar sakogey
  55,36,"Pas aey Jinn-o-Ins (insan),tum apne Rubb ki kin kin qudraton ka inkar karogey"
  55,37,Phir (kya banegi us waqt) jab aasman phatega (split) aur laal chamdey (skin) ki tarah surkh (red) ho jayega
  55,38,Aey Jinn-o-Ins (insan) (us waqt) tum apne Rubb ki kin kin qudraton ko jhutlaogey
  55,39,Us roz kisi Insan aur kisi Jinn se uska gunaah puchne ke zaroorat na hogi
  55,40,Phir (dekh liya jayega ke) tum dono giroh apne Rubb ke kin kin ehsanaat ka inkar karte ho
  55,41,Mujrim wahan apne chehron se pehchan liye jayenge aur unhein peshani ke baal aur paaon pakad pakad kar ghasita jayega
  55,42,Us waqt tum apne Rub ki kin kin qudraton ko jhutlaogey
  55,43,(Us waqt kaha jayega) yeh wahi jahannum hai jisko mujrimeen jhoot karar diya karte thay
  55,44,Usi jahannum aur khaulte (boiling) paani ke darmiyan woh gardish karte rahenge
  55,45,Phir apne Rubb ki kin kin qudraton ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,46,"Aur har us shaks ke liye jo apne Rubb ke huzoor pesh hone ka khauf(darr) rakhta ho, do baagh (gardens) hain"
  55,47,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,48,Hari bhari daaliyon se bharpur
  55,49,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,50,Dono baaghon(gardens) mein do chashmey (springs) rawan
  55,51,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,52,Dono baaghon(gardens) mein har phal ki do qismein
  55,53,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,54,"Jannati log aisey farshon par takiye laga ke baithenge jinke astar dabiz resham ( silk brocade) ke hongey, Aur baagon ki daliyan phalon se jhuki padh rahi hongi"
  55,55,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,56,In niyamaton ke darmiyan sharmili nigahon waliyan hongi jinhein in jannatiyon se pehle kisi insaan ya Jinn ne chuwa na hoga
  55,57,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,58,Aisi khoobsurat jaisey hirey(diamonds) aur Moti
  55,59,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,60,Neki ka badla neki ke siwa aur kya ho sakta hai
  55,61,"Phir aey Jinn-o-Ins (Insan),apne Rubb ke kin kin awsaaf-e-hameeda ka tum inkar karogey"
  55,62,Aur un do baaghon ke alawa do baagh aur hongey
  55,63,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,64,Ghaney sar-sabz o shadaab baagh
  55,65,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,66,Dono baaghon mein do chashmey (springs) fawwaron ki tarah ubaltey (gushing) huey
  55,67,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,68,Un mein ba-kasrat phal aur khajurein aur anaar (pomegranates)
  55,69,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,70,In niyamaton ke darmiyan khoob seerat aur khoobsurat biwiyan
  55,71,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,72,Kheymo (tents) mein theharayi hui hoorein (maidens)
  55,73,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,74,In jannatiyon se pehle kabhi kisi Insaan ya jinn ne unko na chuwa (touch) hoga
  55,75,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,76,Woh jannati sabz-qaleeno (green cushions) aur nafees o nadir farshon (beautiful carpets) par takiye laga ke baithenge
  55,77,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,78,Badi barkat wala hai tere Rubb-e-Jaleel-o-Kareem (Majesty and Glory) ka naam
  56,1,Jab woh honay wala waqia pesh aa jayega
  56,2,To koi uske waquh(occurrence) ko jhutlane wala na hoga
  56,3,Woh tah-o-bala (pasth aur buland) kardene wali aafat hogi
  56,4,Zameen us waqt ek baar hi hila daali jayegi
  56,5,Aur pahad is tarah reza reza kardiye jayenge
  56,6,Ke paraganda (scattered) gubar (dust) ban kar reh jayenge
  56,7,Tum log us waqt teen girohon (jamaat) mein taqseem ho jaogey
  56,8,"Dayein bazu waley, so dayein bazu walon (ke khush-naseebi ) ka kya kehna"
  56,9,"Aur bayein bazu waley, to bayein bazu walon (ki badnasibi ka) kya thikana"
  56,10,Aur aagey waley to phir aagey waley hi hain
  56,11,Wahi to muqarrab (nearest to Allah) log hain
  56,12,Niyamat bhari jannaton mein rahengey
  56,13,Aglon mein se bahut hongey
  56,14,Aur pichlon mein se kam
  56,15,Murassasa takhaton par (On thrones decorated)
  56,16,Takiye lagaye aamne saamne baithengey
  56,17,Unki majlison mein abadi ladke sharab-e-chashma-e jaari se
  56,18,Labrez pyale aur kantar (jugs) aur saagar liye daudte phirte hongey
  56,19,Jisey pee kar na unka sar chakrayega na unki aqal mein fatur (drunkenness) aayega
  56,20,Aur woh unke saamne tarah tarah ke lazeez phal (fruits) pesh karengey jisey chahe chun le
  56,21,Aur parindon ke gosht pesh karenge ke jis parinde ka chahein istimal karein
  56,22,Aur unke liye khubsurat aankhon wali hoorein hongi
  56,23,Aisi haseen jaise chupa kar rakkhey huey moti
  56,24,Yeh sab kuch un aamal ki jaza ke taur par unhein milega jo woh duniya mein karte rahe thay
  56,25,Wahan woh koi behuda kalaam ya gunah ki baat na sunengey
  56,26,Jo baat bhi hogi theek theek hogi
  56,27,"Aur daayein bazu waley, daayein bazu walon ki khush nasibi ka kya kehna"
  56,28,Woh be-khaar (thornless) beriyon(lote trees)
  56,29,Aur teh bar teh chadey huey kelon (bananas)
  56,30,Aur door tak phayli hui chaaon (shadow)
  56,31,Aur har dum rawan (gushing) paani
  56,32,Aur kabhi khatam na honay waley
  56,33,Aur bay rok-tok milne waley ba-kasrat phalon (fruits)
  56,34,Aur unchi nishist gaahon (exalted thrones) mein hongay
  56,35,Unki biwiyon ko hum khaas taur par naye sirey se paida karengey
  56,36,Aur unhein bakira (virgins) bana dengey
  56,37,Apne shoharon ki aashik aur umar mein humsin (equal age)
  56,38,Yeh kuch daayein bazu walon ke liye hai
  56,39,Woh aglon mein se bahut hongey
  56,40,Aur pichlon mein se bhi bahut
  56,41,"Aur baayein (left) bazu wale, bayein bazu walon ki badnasibi ka kya puchna"
  56,42,Woh luu ki lapat (midst of scorching wind) aur khaulte (boiling) huey paani
  56,43,Aur kaalay dhuwon (smoke) ke saaye mein hongey
  56,44,Jo na thanda hoga na aaram de
  56,45,Yeh woh log hongey jo is anjaam ko pahunchne se pehle khush haal thay
  56,46,Aur gunaah-e-azeem par israr karte thay
  56,47,Kehte thay “kya jab hum mar kar khaak ho jayengey aur haddiyon ka panjar reh jayengey to phir utha khadey kiye jayenge
  56,48,Aur kya hamare woh baap dada bhi uthaye jayengey jo pehle guzar chuke hain?”
  56,49,"Aye Nabi in logon se kaho, yaqeenan agle aur pichle sab"
  56,50,Ek din zaroor jama kiye janey wale hain jiska waqt muqarrar kiya ja chuka hai
  56,51,Phir aey gumrahon aur jhutlane walon
  56,52,Tum shajar-e-zaqqum ki giza khane waley ho
  56,53,Usi se tum pait bharogey
  56,54,Aur upar se khaulta (boiling) hua paani
  56,55,Toans (thirst) lagey huey ount (camel) ki tarah piogey
  56,56,Yahi baayein walon ki ziyafat ka saamaan roz-e-jaza mein
  56,57,Humne tumhein paida kiya hai phir kyun tasdeek (confirm) nahin karte
  56,58,"Kabhi tumne gaur kiya, yeh nutfa (sperm) jo tum daltey ho"
  56,59,Usse baccha tum banate ho ya uske banane wale hum hain
  56,60,"Humne tumharey darmiyan maut ko takseem kiya hai, aur hum issey aajiz nahin hai"
  56,61,Ke tumhari shaklein badal dein aur kisi aisi shakal mein tumhein paida kardein jisko tum nahin jante
  56,62,"Apni pehli paidaish ko to tum jante ho, phir kyun sabaq nahin letay"
  56,63,"Kabhi tumne socha, yeh beej (seed) jo tum botey ho"
  56,64,Insey khetiyan tum ugatey ho ya unke ugane waley hum hain
  56,65,Hum chahein to un khetoun ko bhus (rubble) bana kar rakh dein aur tum tarah tarah ki baatein banate reh jao
  56,66,Ke hum par to ulti chatti pad gayi (Lo! we are laden with debt)
  56,67,Balke humarey to naseeb hi phootey huey hain
  56,68,"Kabhi tumne aankhein khol kar dekha, yeh paani jo tum peetey ho"
  56,69,Isey tumne baadal se barsaya hai ya iske barsane wale hum hain
  56,70,"Hum chahein to isey sakht khari(bitter) bana kar rakh dein, phir kyun tum shukar guzar nahin hotey"
  56,71,"Kabhi tumne khayal kiya, yeh aag jo tum sulgate ho"
  56,72,Iska darakht tum ne paida kiya hai ya iske paida karne wale hum hain
  56,73,Humne usko yaad-dihani(reminder) ka zariya aur haajat-mandon (needy) ke liye saaman-e-zeist (provision) banaya hai
  56,74,"Pas aey Nabi, apne Rubb-e-azeem ke naam ki tasbeeh karo"
  56,75,"Pas nahin main kasam khata hoon taaron ke mawake (setting or the mansions, etc.) ki"
  56,76,Agar tum samjho to yeh bahut badi qasam hai
  56,77,Ke yeh ek buland paya Quran hai
  56,78,Ek mehfooz kitaab mein sabt (inscribed)
  56,79,Jisey mutahreen (pure) ke siwa koi choo nahin sakta
  56,80,Yeh Rubb-ul- Aalameen ka nazil karda hai
  56,81,Phir kya is kalam ke saath tum be-atnayi (indifferent) barat-te ho
  56,82,Aur is niyamat mein apna hissa tumne yeh rakkha hai ke isey jhutlate ho
  56,83,To jab marne wale ki jaan halaq tak pahunch chuki hoti hai
  56,84,Aur tum aankhon se dekh rahe hotey ho ke woh marr raha hai
  56,85,Us waqt tumhare ba-nisbat hum uske zyada kareeb hotey hain magar tumko nazar nahin aatey
  56,86,Ab agar tum kisi ke mahkoom(anyones authority) nahin ho aur apne is khayal mein sacchey ho
  56,87,Us waqt uski nikalti hui jaan ko wapas kyun nahin ley aatey
  56,88,Phir woh marne wala agar muqarrabin (near to Allah) mein se hon
  56,89,To uske liye rahat aur umda rizq aur niyamat bhari jannat hai
  56,90,Aur agar woh ashaab-e-yameen mei se ho
  56,91,"To uska istaqbal (welcome) yun hota hai ke salaam hai tujhey, tu ashab-ul-yameen (People on the Right) mein se hai"
  56,92,Aur agar woh jhutlane waley gumraah logon mein se ho
  56,93,To uski tawazu ke liye khaulta (boiling) pani hai
  56,94,Aur jahannum mein jhonka jaana
  56,95,Yeh sab kuch qataii haqq hai
  56,96,Pas aey Nabi apne Rubb-e-Azeem ke naam ki tasbeeh karo
  57,1,"Allah ki tasbeeh ki hai har us cheez ne jo zameen aur aasmano mein hai, Aur wahi zabardast daana (wise) hai"
  57,2,"Zameen aur aasmano ki sultanat ka maalik wahi hai, zindagi bakshta hai aur maut deta hai, aur har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
  57,3,"Wahi awwal bhi hai aur aakhir bhi, aur zaahir bhi hai aur makhfi(hiddin) bhi , aur woh har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai"
  57,4,"Wahi hai jisne aasmano aur zameen ko chey (six) dino mein paida kiya aur phir arsh par jalwa farma hua. Uske ilm mein hai jo kuch zameen mein jata hai aur jo kuch ussey nikalta hai, aur jo kuch aasman se utarta hai aur jo kuch usmein chadhta hai. Woh tumhare saath hai jahan bhi tum ho. Jo kaam bhi karte ho usey woh dekh raha hai"
  57,5,Wahi zameen aur aasmano ki baadshahi ka maalik hai aur tamaam maamlaat faisley ke liye usi ki taraf ruju kiye jatey hain
  57,6,"Wahi raat ko din mein aur din ko raat mein daakhil karta hai, aur dilon ke chupey huye raaz tak janta hai"
  57,7,Iman lao Allah aur uske Rasool par aur kharch karo un cheezon mein se jinpar usney tumko khalifa banaya hai. Jo log tum mein se iman layenge aur maal kharch karenge unke liye bada ajr hai
  57,8,"Tumhein kya ho gaya hai ke tum Allah par iman nahin latey halanke Rasool tumhein apne Rubb par iman laney ki dawat de raha hai, aur woh tumse ahad (covenant) le chuka hai, agar tum waqayi maanne waley ho"
  57,9,Woh Allah hi to hai jo apne banday par saaf saaf aayatein nazil kar raha hai taa-ke tumhein tareekhiyon (darkness) se nikal kar roshni mein le aaye. Aur haqeeat yeh hai ke Allah tumpar nihayat shafeeq aur meharbaan hai
  57,10,Aakhir kya wajah hai ke tum Allah ki raah mein kharch nahin karte halanke zameen aur aasmano ki miraas (inheritance) Allah hi ke liye hai. Tum mein se jo log fatah ke baad kharch aur jihad karenge woh kabhi un logon ke barabar nahin ho sakte jinhon ne fatah se pehle kharch aur jihad kiya hai.Unka darja baad mein kharch aur jihad karne walon se badh-kar hai hai agarche Allah ne dono hi se acchey waade famaye hain. Jo kuch tum karte ho Allah ussey ba-khabar hai
  57,11,Kaun hai jo Allah ko qarz dey? Accha qarz taa-ke Allah usey kai gunaa bada kar wapas dey. Aur uske liye behtareen ajar hai
  57,12,"Us din jabke tum momin mardon aur auraton ko dekhoge ke unka noor unke aagey aagey aur unke dayein jaanib daud raha hoga (unse kaha jayega ke) aaj basharat (khushkhabri) hai. Tumhare liye jannatein hongi jinke nichey nehrein beh rahi hongi, jin mein woh hamesha rahenge. Yahi hai badi kamiyabi"
  57,13,"Us roz munafik mardon aur auraton ka haal yeh hoga ke woh momino se kahenge zara hamari taraf dekho taa-ke hum tumhare noor se kuch fayda uthayein. Magar unse kaha jayega pichey hatt jao, Apna noor kahin aur talash karo. Phir unke darmiyan ek deewar hayal kardi jayegi jismein ek darwaza hoga us darwaze ke andar rehmat hogi aur bahar azaab"
  57,14,"Woh momino se pukar pukar kar kahenge kya hum tumhare saath na thay? Momin jawab dengey haan, magar tumne apne aap ko khud fitne mein dala, mauqa parasti ki, shakk mein padey rahey, aur jhooti tawakkuat (expectations) tumhein fareb deti rahi Yahan tak ke Allah ka faisla aa gaya. Aur aakhri waqt tak woh bada dhoke baaz tumhein Allah ke maamle mein dhoka deta raha"
  57,15,Lihaza aaj na tumse koi fidiya kabool kiya jayega aur na un logon se jinhon ne khula khula kufr kiya tha. Tumhara thikana jahannum hai. Wahi tumhari khabar-giri karne wali hai aur yeh badtareen anjaam hai
  57,16,"Kya iman laney walon ke liye abhi woh waqt nahin aaya ke unke dil Allah ke zikr se pighlein aur uske nazil karda haqq ke aagey jhukein aur woh un logon ki tarah na ho jayein jinhein pehle kitaab di gayi thi, phir ek lambi muddat unpar guzar gayi to unke dil sakht ho gaye aur aaj unmein se aksar fasiq banay huey hain"
  57,17,"Khoob jaan lo ke Allah zameen ko uski maut ke baad zindagi bakshta hai, humne nishaniyan tumko saaf saaf dikha di hai, shayad ke tum aqal se kaam lo"
  57,18,"Mardon aur auraton mein se jo log sadaqaat (charity) dene waley hain aur jinhon ne Allah ko karz-e-hasan diya hai, unko yakeenan kayi gunaa bada kar diya jayega aur unke liye behtareen ajar hai"
  57,19,Aur jo log Allah aur uske Rasoolon par iman laye hain wahi apne Rubb ke nazdeek siddiq aur shaheed hain. Unke liye unka ajar aur unka noor hai. Aur jin logon ne kufr kiya hai aur hamari aayat ko jhutlaya hai woh dozakhi hai
  57,20,Khoob jaan lo ke yeh duniya ki zindagi iske siwa kuch nahin ke ek khel aur dil-lagi aur zaahiri tip top aur tumhara aapas mein ek dusre par fakr jatana aur maal-o-aulad mein ek dusre se badh janey ki koshish karna hai.Iski misal aisi hai jaise ek baarish ho gayi to usse paida honay wali nabataat(vegetation) ko dekh kar kaasht-kaar (kisan) khush ho gaye. Phir wahi kheti pak jati hai aur tum dekhte ho ke woh zard (yellow) ho gayi phir woh bhus (chura chura /crumble) bankar reh jati hai. Iske baraks aakhirat woh jagah hai jahan sakht azaab hai aur Allah ki magfirat aur uski khushnudi hai. Dunkya ki zindagi ek dhoke ke tatti (means of deception) ke siwa kuch nahin
  57,21,"Daudo (race) aur ek dusrey se aage badhne ki koshish karo apne Rubb ki magfirat aur uski jannat ki taraf jiski wussat (width) aasman-o-zameen jaisi hai. Jo muhayya ki gayi hai un logon ke liye jo Allah aur uske Rasoolon par iman laye hon. Yeh Allah ka fazl hai, jisey chahta hai ata farmata hai, aur Allah badey fazl wala hai"
  57,22,Koi museebat aisi nahin hai jo zameen mein ya tumhare apne nafs par nazil hoti ho aur humne usko paida karne se pehle ek kitaab mein likh na rakkha ho. Aisa karna Allah ke liye bahut aasaan kaam hai
  57,23,(Yeh sab kuch isliye hai) taa-ke jo kuch bhi nuksaan tumhein ho us par tum dil-shikasta (grieve) na hon aur jo kuch Allah tumhein ata farmaye uspar phool na jao. Allah aisey logon ko pasand nahin karta jo apne aap ko badi cheez samajhte hain aur fakr jatate hain
  57,24,Jo khud bukhl (niggard/kanjusi) karte hain aur dusron ko bukhl par uksate hain. Ab agar koi ru-gardani (mooh pherna) karta hai to Allah be-niyaz aur satoda siffat (immensely praiseworthy) hai
  57,25,"Humne apne Rasoolon ko saaf saaf nishaniyon aur hidayaat ke saath bheja, aur unke saath kitaab aur mizaan (balance) nazil ki taakay log insaf par qayam hon. Aur loha (Iron) utara jis mein bada zoar hai aur logon ke liye munafa hai. Yeh isliye kiya gaya hai ke Allah ko maloom ho jaye ke kaun usko dekhe bagair uski aur uske rasoolon ki madad karta hai. Yaqeenan Allah badi quwwat wala aur zabardast hai"
  57,26,Humne Nooh aur Ibrahim ko bheja aur un dono ki nasal mein nabuwat aur kitaab rakh di phir unki aulad mein se kisi ne hidayat ikhtiyar ki aur bahut se faasiq ho gaye
  57,27,"Unke baad humne pai dar pai (succession) apne Rasool bheje, aur in sabke baad Isa ibn-e-Maryam ko maboos kiya aur usko Injil ata ki, aur jin logon ne uski pairvi ikhtiyar ki unke dilon mein humne taras (tenderness ) aur reham daal diya. Aur rahbaniyat (monasticism) unhon ne khud ijaad karli, humne usey unpar farz nahin kiya tha. Magar Allah ki khushnudi ki talab mein unhon ne aap hi yeh bidaat nikali aur phir iski pabandi karne ka jo haqq tha usey ada na kiya. Unmein se jo log iman laye huye thay unka ajr humne unko ata kiya, magar unmein se aksar log faasiq hain"
  57,28,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, Allah se daro aur uske Rasool par iman lao. Allah tumhein apni Rehmat ka dohra hissa ata farmyega aur tumhein wahi noor bakhshega jiski roshni mein tum chaloge, aur tumhare kasoor maaf kardega.Allah bada maaf karne wala aur meharbaan hai"
  57,29,"(Tumko yeh rawish ikhtiyar karni chahiye) taa-ke ehle kitaab ko maalom ho jaye ke Allah ke fazal par unka koi ijara (control/ikhtiyar) nahin hai, aur yeh ke Allah ka fazal uske apne hi haath mein hai, Jisey chahta hai ata farmata hai. Aur woh badey fazal(bounty) wala hai"